<i>noun</i>: 회한 [회ː한/훼ː한], 뉘우침 [뉘우침] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>회한 [회ː한/훼ː한]</dt><br>
<dd>regret; remorse; contrition</dd><br>
<dd>잘못 등을 뉘우치고 한숨을 쉬며 탄식함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of letting out a sigh and grieving while regretting one's wrongdoings.</dd><br>
<dt>뉘우침 [뉘우침]</dt><br>
<dd>repentance; penitence; contrition</dd><br>
<dd>스스로 자신의 잘못을 깨닫고 반성함.</dd><br>
<dd>Realizing one's fault and reflecting on oneself and one's behavior.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>